# IndieCaster Astro Project Structure

## Key Files and Directories

### Configuration
- [astro.config.mjs](mdc:astro.config.mjs) - Astro configuration
- [src/content.config.ts](mdc:src/content.config.ts) - Content collections schema
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Dependencies and scripts

### Content Management
- `src/content/episodes/` - Episode markdown files
- `src/content/guests/` - Guest markdown files
- [docs/schemas.md](mdc:docs/schemas.md) - Schema documentation

### Pages and Routing
- [src/pages/index.astro](mdc:src/pages/index.astro) - Homepage
- [src/pages/episodes.astro](mdc:src/pages/episodes.astro) - Episodes listing
- [src/pages/episodes/[slug].astro](mdc:src/pages/episodes/[slug].astro) - Individual episode pages
- [src/pages/about.astro](mdc:src/pages/about.astro) - About page
- [src/pages/contact.astro](mdc:src/pages/contact.astro) - Contact page

### Components
- [src/components/](mdc:src/components/) - Reusable Astro components
- [src/layouts/](mdc:src/layouts/) - Page layouts

### Static Assets
- `public/audio/episodes/` - Episode audio files
- `public/episode-artwork/` - Episode artwork images
- `public/profile-images/` - Guest profile pictures
- `public/icons/` - UI icons and player controls

### Styles
- [src/styles/](mdc:src/styles/) - CSS files and design system
- [src/styles/base.css](mdc:src/styles/base.css) - Base styles
- [src/styles/custom-properties.css](mdc:src/styles/custom-properties.css) - CSS custom properties

### Scripts
- [scripts/create-episode.js](mdc:scripts/create-episode.js) - Episode generator
- [scripts/create-guest.js](mdc:scripts/create-guest.js) - Guest generator

## Development Workflow
1. Use generator scripts for new content: `npm run create-episode` or `npm run create-guest`
2. Follow schema definitions in [docs/schemas.md](mdc:docs/schemas.md)
3. Add media files to appropriate `public/` directories
4. Build and test with `npm run dev` and `npm run build`
